Now, switch to the ![latest version (1.4.6) of Biz Analyst for Android](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=in.bizanalyst). Enjoy analyzing your data and day to day activities with simplicity:

# Configuration to view preview of PDF before sharing

+ We have added a configuration to preview the PDF file that you are about to share. Configuration to view PDF preview before sharing (Settings -> Share)
+ Configuration to share narration in ledger report (Settings -> Ledger Report)
+ View the HSN code in Items, Stock Group list and Item Summary screen
+ In PDF Invoice, added Bill of lading no & LR no
+ In ledger report, click on closing balance to scroll to bottom & click on opening balance to scroll to top
+ Email address is pre-filled while sharing by email if email is set in tally
+ Fixed auto data-sync issue for some phones
